522
00:29:47,286 --> 00:29:49,413
DERIVATION:
WHETHER ONE WAS CREATED BASED ON THE OTHER

523
00:29:49,496 --> 00:29:52,291
The plaintiff's Fiesta
was announced in October 2024

524
00:29:52,374 --> 00:29:53,875
and shown in November of that year,

525
00:29:53,959 --> 00:29:56,169
which was covered by many media outlets.

526
00:29:56,253 --> 00:29:59,881
Thus, it would be reasonable to infer
that the defendant saw Fiesta in person

527
00:29:59,965 --> 00:30:01,967
and through various outlets
during its exhibition

528
00:30:02,050 --> 00:30:04,386
before using it to produce Amusement Park.

529
00:30:05,262 --> 00:30:07,055
If the defendant's Amusement Park

530
00:30:07,139 --> 00:30:09,641
was actually produced
before the plaintiff's Fiesta,

531
00:30:09,725 --> 00:30:12,644
that would constitute the plaintiff's
imitation of the defendant's work.

532
00:30:12,728 --> 00:30:15,230
Amusement Park was completed
in March 2024,

533
00:30:15,314 --> 00:30:17,190
before Fiesta was announced.

534
00:30:17,274 --> 00:30:19,776
The defendant's argument
is purely arbitrary.

535
00:30:20,402 --> 00:30:22,446
The defendant has not submitted
any objective evidence

536
00:30:22,529 --> 00:30:24,448
that proves when Amusement Park
was completed.

537
00:30:24,531 --> 00:30:25,907
That is not true.

538
00:30:25,991 --> 00:30:27,826
The defendant
made a sale of Amusement Park

539
00:30:27,909 --> 00:30:30,454
at a flea market
prior to the announcement of Fiesta.

540
00:30:30,537 --> 00:30:33,790
The person claiming to have purchased
the defendant's work is Ms. Hwang Ye-jin,

541
00:30:33,874 --> 00:30:36,501
but her testimony lacks credibility.

542
00:30:36,585 --> 00:30:38,420
The brief outlines
the reasoning in detail.

543
00:30:38,503 --> 00:30:39,880
Yes.

544
00:30:39,963 --> 00:30:43,592
The credibility concern raised
regarding Ms. Hwang's testimony,

545
00:30:43,675 --> 00:30:46,261
based on her relationship
with Ms. Lee Seo-yeong, is acknowledged.

546
00:30:46,345 --> 00:30:49,014
The court also acknowledges
the testimonies of their acquaintances

547
00:30:49,097 --> 00:30:50,349
that support this concern.

548
00:30:51,850 --> 00:30:55,687
Does the defense counsel
have any other objective evidence,

549
00:30:55,771 --> 00:30:58,565
aside from Ms. Hwang Ye-jin's testimony
that she purchased Amusement Park

550
00:30:58,648 --> 00:31:00,484
at a flea market in April 2024?

551
00:31:00,567 --> 00:31:01,693
We do.

552
00:31:02,194 --> 00:31:04,154
To provide such evidence,
we ask the court to allow

553
00:31:04,237 --> 00:31:06,740
party examination of the plaintiff
and the defendant

554
00:31:06,823 --> 00:31:08,116
as outlined in the brief.

555
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:15,832
FIESTA BY RYU GWAN-MO
AMUSEMENT PARK BY MOON JEONG-HYE

556
00:31:15,916 --> 00:31:17,417
It appears that in Fiesta,

557
00:31:17,501 --> 00:31:19,878
