00:35:17,949 --> 00:35:21,244
Are you unaware
of such basic procedural rules?

626
00:35:32,631 --> 00:35:36,384
You just need to tell us
the intention behind your painting.

627
00:35:38,094 --> 00:35:39,179
I don't know.

628
00:35:45,393 --> 00:35:46,478
What's wrong with her?

629
00:35:49,064 --> 00:35:50,357
Ms. Moon.

630
00:35:50,440 --> 00:35:52,567
All your paintings utilize vivid colors.

631
00:35:52,651 --> 00:35:54,778
Can you tell us how you came to use

632
00:35:54,861 --> 00:35:56,946
a wider range of colors
than what meets the eye?

633
00:35:57,030 --> 00:35:59,491
I… don't know.

