00:36:24,307 --> 00:36:26,810
Forgive… She's asking for forgiveness?

641
00:36:26,893 --> 00:36:29,187
-You say that…
-Did she just confess?

642
00:36:29,729 --> 00:36:31,189
…after you tarnish my name?

