688
00:39:17,939 --> 00:39:20,483
She falls under my jurisdiction
as my associate.

689
00:39:21,359 --> 00:39:24,988
Gosh… What a touching moment
between colleagues.

690
00:39:26,614 --> 00:39:28,575
No more screw-ups!

691
00:39:36,958 --> 00:39:38,251
I'm sorry, sir.

