700
00:40:05,403 --> 00:40:08,156
Maybe she thought
it was just miscommunication.

701
00:40:09,908 --> 00:40:12,327
You also had so little time to prep.

702
00:40:13,620 --> 00:40:14,662
What now?

703
00:40:16,039 --> 00:40:19,250
I wouldn't have put her
on the stand if I had known.

704
00:40:20,585 --> 00:40:21,794
It's over already.

705
00:40:23,796 --> 00:40:25,089
When the court reconvenes,

706
00:40:25,173 --> 00:40:27,842
cite health issues
to end party examination.

707
00:40:28,968 --> 00:40:31,262
Okay.

708
00:40:31,346 --> 00:40:32,388
What?

709
00:40:34,223 --> 00:40:35,475
Intellectual disability?

