00:41:07,465 --> 00:41:10,426
We can verify it through
the defendant's history of works

722
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:11,386
with a unified style.

723
00:41:11,469 --> 00:41:14,806
If we want to confirm that such works
were indeed produced by the defendant

724
00:41:14,889 --> 00:41:18,434
and not created recently
after the incident in question,

725
00:41:18,518 --> 00:41:20,979
it is crucial to have
the defendant testify.

726
00:41:21,062 --> 00:41:25,149
-Yes, but--
-Since the defendant is in attendance,

727
00:41:25,233 --> 00:41:28,403
I believe it would be best
to proceed with the examination.

728
00:41:28,486 --> 00:41:30,738
If the court deems her
physically unable to continue,

729
00:41:30,822 --> 00:41:33,908
the court will exercise its authority
to suspend the proceedings.

730
00:41:40,498 --> 00:41:43,584
Ms. Moon,
have you ever taken an art lesson?

731
00:41:44,961 --> 00:41:47,630
Your testimony is being recorded,
so please answer aloud.

732
00:41:49,173 --> 00:41:51,009
-Yes.
-And where did you take it?

733
00:41:51,634 --> 00:41:52,844
Jumi Art Academy…

734
00:41:52,927 --> 00:41:54,303
Please speak louder.

735
00:41:54,387 --> 00:41:56,681
At Jumi Art Academy.

736
00:41:57,724 --> 00:41:58,975
Your Honor,

737
00:41:59,058 --> 00:42:01,102
Jumi Art Academy is
a neighborhood establishment

738
00:42:01,185 --> 00:42:02,311
led by a non-expert.

739
00:42:02,979 --> 00:42:03,980
All right.

740
00:42:05,898 --> 00:42:08,776
Do you know a Yoo Seong-eun
who also attends the academy?

741
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:11,195
-Yes.
-Please answer clearly.

742
00:42:11,279 --> 00:42:12,613
Yes!

743
00:42:13,740 --> 00:42:15,533
According to Ms. Yoo,

744
00:42:15,616 --> 00:42:19,287
the academy students
often visited art fairs and exhibitions

745
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:22,623
