when my mom turns off the lights.

872
00:52:19,928 --> 00:52:21,055
My dad's face.

873
00:52:23,682 --> 00:52:24,600
I like it.

874
00:52:26,352 --> 00:52:27,770
It makes me happy.

875
00:52:30,105 --> 00:52:33,192
Drawing his face makes me happy

876
00:52:33,275 --> 00:52:36,654
and so does looking at a painting of him.

877
00:52:40,199 --> 00:52:43,369
Jeong-hye loves her mom
more than anyone else in the world.

878
00:52:43,452 --> 00:52:45,287
Her world revolves around her mom.

879
00:52:49,333 --> 00:52:52,461
-Jeong-hye is a special person.
