00:52:52,544 --> 00:52:54,129
Her intellectual abilities aren't low.

881
00:52:54,213 --> 00:52:56,256
-It may be more accurate to say…
-Jeong-hye.

882
00:52:56,340 --> 00:52:57,925
-Don't listen to him.
-…that her talents

883
00:52:58,008 --> 00:53:00,052
