can detect 100 million colors.

887
00:53:11,522 --> 00:53:12,940
Truly a flawless eye for color.

888
00:53:14,608 --> 00:53:17,861
And with her genius skills,
she just wanted to draw

889
00:53:17,945 --> 00:53:19,196
one thing.

890
00:53:20,364 --> 00:53:21,573
The father she missed.

