920
00:55:19,983 --> 00:55:20,943
Here.

921
00:55:55,686 --> 00:55:57,020
My poor baby.

922
00:56:00,023 --> 00:56:01,358
Jeong-hye.

923
00:56:04,862 --> 00:56:05,863
Right.

924
00:56:07,447 --> 00:56:09,616
I'm sorry.

925
00:56:11,159 --> 00:56:13,579
I really didn't know…

926
00:56:14,371 --> 00:56:15,664
I didn't know…

927
00:56:23,171 --> 00:56:25,507
you missed your dad that much.

928
00:56:29,511 --> 00:56:31,972
So that's why you did that.

929
00:56:32,472 --> 00:56:35,642
That's why every time
you finished a painting,

930
00:56:36,351 --> 00:56:39,146
