931
00:56:43,901 --> 00:56:45,277
Jeong-hye, it's okay.

932
00:56:46,278 --> 00:56:48,322
You can miss him.

933
00:56:48,405 --> 00:56:51,450
You can draw him.

934
00:56:52,242 --> 00:56:53,118
And also…

935
00:56:55,579 --> 00:56:57,831
