936
00:56:58,457 --> 00:56:59,499
It's all okay.

937
00:57:06,173 --> 00:57:07,049
Jeong-hye.

938
00:57:08,967 --> 00:57:13,221
If I ask you about your paintings
in the courtroom,

939
