You can tell everyone
about how you drew your dad.

942
00:57:27,319 --> 00:57:28,820
I promise I'm okay with it.

943
00:57:29,863 --> 00:57:30,739
Okay?

944
00:57:31,531 --> 00:57:32,866
-Okay?
