1038
01:03:26,303 --> 01:03:27,679
I'm glad it all worked out.

1039
01:03:28,221 --> 01:03:29,556
MY SISTER

1040
01:03:29,639 --> 01:03:32,976
Jeong-hye's paintings always seemed
full of happiness,

1041
01:03:33,059 --> 01:03:35,228
so I never knew she lived
with such longing.

1042
01:03:35,979 --> 01:03:36,938
Yeah.

1043
01:03:37,522 --> 01:03:40,775
Did you know Jeong-hye was an art prodigy?

1044
01:03:43,111 --> 01:03:43,987
No.

1045
01:03:45,155 --> 01:03:47,449
If I were a prodigy like Jeong-hye,

1046
01:03:47,532 --> 01:03:49,909
would Auntie have raised me
despite my disability?

1047
01:03:54,164 --> 01:03:55,707
I'm sorry, Hyo-ju.

1048
01:03:59,085 --> 01:04:01,302
I'M SORRY, HYO-JU

1049
01:04:04,341 --> 01:04:07,052
Mom also regrets sending you away.

1050
01:04:11,806 --> 01:04:13,088
MOM ALSO REGRETS SENDING YOU AWAY

1051
01:04:15,310 --> 01:04:16,644
Any recent photos of Auntie?

1052
01:04:20,190 --> 01:04:21,149
Why do you ask?

1053
01:04:21,691 --> 01:04:22,984
Do you miss Mom?

1054
01:04:24,903 --> 01:04:27,989
Of course I do. She gave birth to me.

1055
01:04:30,200 --> 01:04:31,534
Then why don't you visit her?

1056
01:04:34,162 --> 01:04:39,000
Probably for the same reason
why Jeong-hye hid her dad's face

1057
01:04:39,084 --> 01:04:40,251
in her paintings.

1058
01:04:40,335 --> 01:04:42,670
I'm more worried about my mom being sad

1059
01:04:42,754 --> 01:04:45,757
than I am about getting to see Auntie.

1060
01:04:46,883 --> 01:04:49,552
My mom and dad use sign language.

1061
01:04:49,636 --> 01:04:51,012
I'm the only one reading lips.

1062
01:04:51,638 --> 01:04:55,308
They want to make it look like
I can hear when I see Auntie and Uncle.

1063
01:04:56,226 --> 01:04:58,853
I think Jeong-hye's mother
was like that too.

1064
01:04:59,354 --> 01:05:01,856
Is that what a parent's love is like?

1065
01:05:07,779 --> 01:05:09,218
IS THAT WHAT A PARENT'S LOVE IS LIKE?

1066
01:05:17,831 --> 01:05:19,290
-What's going on?
-Hey.

1067
01:05:19,374 --> 01:05:21,376
There's supposed to be
a big announcement today.

1068
01:05:32,512 --> 01:05:34,764
Wow, the named partners.

1069
01:05:35,640 --> 01:05:36,683
Who?

1070
01:05:37,475 --> 01:05:39,477
Yullim is Shin, Ko & Kim.

1071
01:05:39,561 --> 01:05:42,188
-Right.
-Mr. Shin Myeong-jin.

1072
01:05:42,272 --> 01:05:44,441
Mr. Ko Seung-cheol.

1073
01:05:44,524 --> 01:05:46,693
And Mr. Kim Yul-seong.

1074
01:05:47,652 --> 01:05:50,613
Since time is money for everyone here,

1075
01:05:50,697 --> 01:05:51,656
I'll keep this short.

1076
01:05:51,739 --> 01:05:55,034
I've gathered you
for an important announcement.

1077
01:05:55,618 --> 01:05:59,289
As of today, I'll be retired
but staying on as an advisor.

1078
01:06:01,207 --> 01:06:02,167
What's going on here?

1079
01:06:02,250 --> 01:06:04,377
Now, I'd like to introduce my successor,

1080
01:06:05,378 --> 01:06:09,340
our new managing partner.

1081
01:06:09,924 --> 01:06:11,468
Ms. Kwon Na-yeon.

1082
01:06:12,510 --> 01:06:13,803
Please step up.

1083
01:06:13,887 --> 01:06:16,097
The attorney whose name
is a brand in itself?

1084
01:07:21,287 --> 01:07:24,499
BEYOND THE BAR

1085
01:07:24,582 --> 01:07:27,210
My ex-boyfriend did this to me.

1086
01:07:27,293 --> 01:07:28,711
I want to sue him.

1087
01:07:28,795 --> 01:07:31,422
If the client did not consent
to the sadistic act,

1088
01:07:31,506 --> 01:07:33,675
it could constitute assault.

1089
01:07:33,758 --> 01:07:35,343
To establish assault,

1090
01:07:35,426 --> 01:07:37,929
we'd have to argue
that the consent was not valid.

1091
01:07:38,012 --> 01:07:40,932
Can't we say love is
a form of diminished capacity too?

1092
01:07:42,183 --> 01:07:43,518
Let me get you some new ones.

1093
01:07:46,229 --> 01:07:48,439
I didn't realize you were
the opposing counsel,

1094
01:07:48,523 --> 01:07:50,156
so I said more than I should have.

1095
01:07:50,233 --> 01:07:51,526
How do you know Mr. Jung?

1096
01:07:51,609 --> 01:07:53,820
Forming a close relationship
with the opposing party

1097
01:07:53,903 --> 01:07:55,780
violates the duty
to uphold professional dignity.

1098
01:07:55,863 --> 01:07:58,157
What are you doing
acting like some cheap attorney?

1099
01:07:58,241 --> 01:08:00,201
The chances of winning this case are slim.

1100
01:08:03,999 --> 01:08:05,999
Subtitle translation by Justin S. Kim

